<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>With that said.. I like the ideas some people have had of reducing the effectiveness of a charmed mob. Lower it’s regen. Lower its damage output. Heck, lower its health. (Although I could see that being used to soften up a mob, then break charm and get an easy kill.)<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
