<br>
- I agree Command of Druzzil is overpowering in it's current form. (Perhaps that's the part you didn't understand in my first post today.)<br>
<br>
- I think the ideas of lowering the overall power of charmed mobs is the best all around solution.<br>
<br>
You are STILL trying to paint a clouded picture here:<br>
